### VaxTrace Cloud — VS Code REST Client
### Install extension: humao.rest-client
### Click "Send Request" above each request

@base = http://localhost:7071/api

### ── Health Check ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/health

###

### ── Submit Format A vaccination (JSON body) ─────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "format": "A",
  "id": "8001015009087",
  "vaccinationCenter": "Charlotte Maxeke Hospital",
  "vaccinationDate": "2024-01-20",
  "vaccineSerialNumber": "JNJ-2024-002-A"
}

###

### ── Submit Format A vaccination (raw message string) ────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination
Content-Type: text/plain

9203224800088:Inkosi Albert Luthuli Hospital:2024-01-10:AZ-2024-003-A

###

### ── Submit Format B vaccination (raw message string) ────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination
Content-Type: text/plain

BAR-00001:2024-02-12:Groote Schuur Hospital:0105215359081

###

### ── Submit Format B vaccination (JSON body) ─────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "format": "B",
  "vaccineBarcode": "BAR-99999",
  "vaccinationDate": "2024-03-15",
  "vaccinationCenter": "Tygerberg Hospital",
  "id": "7512086150082"
}

###

### ── Query by SA ID (pre-seeded, fully vaccinated) ───────────────────────
GET {{base}}/vaccination/0105215359081

###

### ── Query by SA ID (pre-seeded, partially vaccinated) ───────────────────
GET {{base}}/vaccination/8001015009087

###

### ── Query by passport number ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/vaccination/P12345678

###

### ── Query non-existent ID (should return 404) ───────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/vaccination/0000000000000

###

### ── Invalid message (should return 400) ─────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination
Content-Type: text/plain

this is not a valid vaccination message

###

### ── Bulk ingest (Format A and B mixed) ──────────────────────────────────
POST {{base}}/vaccination/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

[
  "8001015009087:Life Hilton Private Hospital:2024-04-01:PFZ-2024-100",
  "BAR-88001:2024-04-05:Netcare Blaauwberg Hospital:9203224800088",
  "P12345678:Groote Schuur Hospital:2024-04-10:AZ-2024-200",
  "0407145189089:Steve Biko Academic Hospital:2024-04-15:MOD-2024-050"
]

###

### ── Get processing stats ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{base}}/vaccination/stats

###
